title: Tom Brady news & 2015 rookie predictions
itunes:title: Tom Brady news & 2015 rookie predictions
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- react to the latest in the Tom Brady suspension saga (7:35) and more news from around the NFL. The guys also make their 2015 rookie predictions (29:30) and project the starting lineups in the AFC East (42:45).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
